{"type":"article_comment","id":488671,"parentType":"article","parentId":23733,"uid":43432,"contents":"班公錯高地戰最新發展<br>\n目前印度軍方佔據地理優勢，班公錯(Pangong Tso)南部高地基地為主，直接往南方曼冬錯(Spanggur Tso)的中國解放軍據點監視，包括戰車聚集地、防衛陣地等，皆在印度之下，進一步可能執行山地突擊行動<br>\n<br>\n印度陸軍裝甲部隊控制曼冬錯山谷，那是可能突圍的關卡，往下還有印軍據點監視，簡單來說中國解放軍陷入被動狀態，若不撤退，軍隊很可能會被包圍<br>\n<br>\n尤其，班公錯南部高地基地是圖博士兵為主，很可能會再度肉搏夜襲位在班公錯東岸的解放軍士兵陣地，而且情況會很危險，因為解放軍的後勤隨時會被印軍截斷<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/jTut9xF_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jTut9xF_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jTut9xF_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wnmOUry_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wnmOUry_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wnmOUry_d.webp?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=30435untrusted fake 2049bbsbook.com/story.php?story_fbid=304352840662771&amp;id=100032641718395</a>\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n</a><div class=\"meta\"><a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=30435untrusted fake 2049bbsbook.com/story.php?story_fbid=304352840662771&amp;id=100032641718395</a>\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"pull-right aw-small-text\">2020-09-03</span>\n<span class=\"operate aw-vote-ui\">\n</span></a><a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"agree disabled\">\n<i class=\"icon icon-agree\"></i> <b class=\"count\">9</b>\n</a>\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a href=\"/vote/log/item_type-article_comment__item_id-488671\" class=\"aw-small-text\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"icon icon-users